            reckoned with. Another player who was a staple of the modern game mimicked MJ himself. Kobe Bryant
            practically had the same game was Michael Jordan, exciting above the rim play and an unstoppable turnaround
            jumper. Kobe was the closest thing we would see to a Jordan due to the similarity of how they approached the
            game of basketball. If Kobe was the closest thing we had to a Jordan, Lebron James would be the closest
            thing we would have to Jordan’s greatness. Lebron to many is the only player who can surpass Jordan’s
            greatness. Lebron is an athletic Freak, 6’9 who is basically a Swiss army knife. Lebron can basically do
            everything defend, score, rebound, pass, be a leader, play long minutes etc. Lebron James is the most
            versatile player the game has ever seen and it is why he has the case to be the greatest to have ever played
            the game.
